* {{ill|Akaiiwa Shrine|ja|赤猪岩神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ( [[Tottori Prefecture|Nanbu Town,]] [[:ja:西伯郡|Saihaku District,]] [[:ja:南部町_(鳥取県)|Tottori Prefecture]] ) * {{ill|Miyagi Suwa Shrine|ja|宮木諏訪神社}} ( [[Nagano Prefecture|Tatsuno Town,]] [[:ja:上伊那郡|Kamiina District,]] [[Nagano Prefecture]] ) == See Also ==
* {{ill|Ame-no-Fuyukinu|ja|天之冬衣神|1=Ame-no-Fuyukinu|en|6=simple|7=User:Immanuelle/Ame-no-Fuyukinu|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Sashikuni Okami|lt=Sashikuni Ōkami|ja|刺国大神|en:draft|6=simple|7=User:Immanuelle/Sashikuni_Okami|8=fr|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * [[Ōkuninushi|Okuninushi]]
